                                                                                                                                Messaging

                                                                                                                                Snackbar

                                                                                                                                A snackbar is an ephemeral message used to give users feedback after taking an action.

                                                                                                                                Usage
                                                                                                                                Content
                                                                                                                                Specs
                                                                                                                                Status & changelog

                                                                                                                                Metrics

                                                                                                                                Type and color

                                                                                                                                Colors in button states

                                                                                                                                Pressed state
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Button state colors inside Snackbars are calculated programmatically. They need to be customized to work on the color token InverseBackgroundTeriary at black + 20% white.

                                                                                                                                Button on colors
                                                                                                                                Spec for buttons on various background color tokens

                                                                                                                                Announcement:

                                                                                                                                Announce the message when it appears on screen.

                                                                                                                                Focus:

                                                                                                                                For simple Snackbars that don’t have a button, don’t change the focus to the Snackbar.

                                                                                                                                With a button
                                                                                                                                Add notes

                                                                                                                                Voiced preview: "A thing happened. Actions available.”


                                                                                                                                Label: [Message text]

                                                                                                                                Trait: Static text


                                                                                                                                Announcement:

                                                                                                                                Announce the message when it appears on screen.


                                                                                                                                Focus:

                                                                                                                                Focus on element 1 when it appears. With the snackbar focused, it should NOT start to time out on its own until the user focuses away or completes an action in the actions menu.

                                                                                                                                Open question: I would like the focus to return to the item that triggered the snackbar, but not sure if possible from the component level.
